# Cloudflare Pages already serves clean URLs automatically:
#   /contact          works and shows contact.html
#   /contact.html     auto-redirects to /contact
#
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT redirect a clean URL (e.g. /contact) back to its .html
# file. Cloudflare's built-in .html->clean redirect plus a clean->.html rule
# creates an infinite redirect loop ("ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS"), which is why
# the Contact page would not load.

# Friendly alias that does not collide with Cloudflare's clean URLs:
/home    /    301
